    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a bonus action, you reach your spiritual apotheosis and embody your patron ancestor’s spirit completely. You and your Exemplar Companion creatures gain the following benefits for 1 minute:</p><ul><li><p>You have advantage on all ability checks.</p></li><li><p>When you take the Attack action on your turn, you can do one of the following as part of that action: take the Dash, Help, or Use an Object action, or attempt to shove a creature, grapple a creature, or escape a grapple.</p></li><li><p>When you regain hit points, treat any dice rolled to determine the hit points you regain as having rolled their maximum value for you.</p></li></ul><p>Once you use this feature, you can’t do so again until you finish a long rest, unless you expend a 5th-level spell slot to use it again.</p>",
